short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is used by WinTask to automate browser actions. It is not intended to be used as a standalone extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
WinTask component browser automation for Wintask V7.4 + .
This extension is to be used in conjugation with WinTask software, it allows the WinTask software to communicate with the browser in order to execute multiple actions like writing and clicking html elements.
It's not intended to be used as standalone extension!
